# Gitflow Workflow Rules

- Once fully finished with the task create a pull request
- Create pull request in a semantic compatible formatting like: 
```
feat(portfolio): [YV-12345] ticket title
```
- Make sure to use either: commitlint rulese when creating a PR found in .cursor.json file
- Make sure to add a very short description to a PR of what has been done
- Make sure the description is super basic, and in a natural language
